    "methodology": "Base salary drawn from salaries-india.json (median monthly USD). Statutory contributions calculated on base salary at rates sourced from EPFO, ESIC, and Payment of Gratuity Act (all accessed May 2026). EPF calculated on basic salary assumed at 40% of gross CTC (common employer practice). ESI does not apply to any role in this dataset as all gross wages exceed the ₹21,000/month statutory threshold. Gratuity accrual modeled at 4.81% of basic salary per Payment of Gratuity Act formula (15/26 × basic per year). Equipment amortized over 36 months. Management overhead is an industry-typical estimate (5–10%) for organizations using managed remote workforce providers; this figure is not a quoted rate from any specific provider."
  },
